3,"uid":127033,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T19:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/034500_69b3492b8e5fb10b549470b0928c0cfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F034500_69b3492b8e5fb10b549470b0928c0cfc.png&h=f081cb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n場地突然一震將兩者分隔開一段距離<br />\n異形慢慢行近 一跳將蚊蚊蚊捉實<br />\n蚊蚊蚊嬌喘一聲倒在異形嘅懷裡，喺呢個時候，蚊蚊蚊眼如微絲，濕潤嘅雙唇，微微張開，口中噴出有如蘭花一樣嘅香氣，對住如斯尤物，佛都會動心啦。異形一手抱腰，另一隻手也不閒住喎，偷偷地從蚊蚊蚊衣襟挖入，係佢豐滿既雙峰附近，周&shy;圍任意遊覽。而蚊蚊蚊既慾火再也控制不住，果兩個釘，亦由軟既棉&shy;花糖變為硬既橡皮糖啦。"},{"pid":"5da648365ef116ded78e6a807345c710bbf11f73","tid":752303,"uid":127033,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T19:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/035356_4e7529c02665ab97fe6beece037dca60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F035356_4e7529c02665ab97fe6beece037dca60.png&h=0d6b599f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食宵夜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於唔洗食蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c80ccb9002e5d45d01326f8215480f3f1682c5","tid":752303,"uid":143959,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T19:58:37.000Z","msg":"以為你捕獲到煮牛扒個蚊蚊蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622d40a37db91d7e1f7434ede0ffc9fa34e2df0e","tid":752303,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T20:06:31.000Z","msg":"以為咩咁勁<br />\n樓豬唔係唔g 咩係蜘蛛呀？"},{"pid":"27c17b7673b94f619daa7474bdcf6779719d6a60","tid":752303,"uid":127033,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/193159_dd58fd3142352932d50d19624a16868a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2